Feature: Build gatling report description

    As Xray Connector,
    I want to enrich a gatling test execution report with information from gatling
    So that I may provide more information to the user in Xray

    Scenario: Enrich report with simulation information, URL and simulation results details

        Given The reference test plan is 'DEFAULT_TEST_PLAN'
        And   The gatling reports directory is 'test/fixtures/reports/gatling/report-description'
        And   The gatling report url is 'GATLING_REPORT_URL'
        And   The gatling simulation main class is 'GenericTest'
        And   The test plan file is 'test/fixtures/reports/gatling/report-description/test-plan.json'
        When  Xray Connector builds the report description
        Then  The report description should be the same as file 'test/fixtures/reports/gatling/report-description/description.txt'
